(2, 1, '2013-06-19 16:27:41', '2013-06-19 16:27:41', 'Pleasure Solution is experts in Web Design and Development Services.\r\n\r\nPleasure Solutions is a rapidly growing CMS (WordPress, Joomla, Drupal), web solutions and custom application development company.\r\n\r\nOur business approach is based on close collaboration with our clients to ensure that the implementation of each technology is always aligned with their broader business objectives.\r\n\r\nOur efficient development processes, strong communication skills and talented personnel combined with a track record of successful projects and satisfied clients are just a few indicators of our strengths.', 'Company', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'company', '', '', '2013-06-22 16:42:21', '2013-06-22 16:42:21', '', 0, 'http://www.pleasuresolutions.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
