(49, 1, '2013-06-19 17:54:01', '2013-06-19 17:54:01', 'WordPress is one of the world’s most popular and robust content management systems. Using WordPress is an affordable way to gain control over your website without using a full web developer for changes and updates.\r\n\r\nWordPress is web software you can use to create a beautiful website or blog. We like to say that WordPress is both free and priceless at the same time.', 'WordPress Development', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress-development', '', '', '2013-07-02 10:01:37', '2013-07-02 10:01:37', '', 0, 'http://www.pleasuresolutions.com/?p=49', 0, 'post', '', 0),
